creator: Carsharing Russia
descriptionHtml:
Delimobil is a carsharing service available for drivers over the age of 19 and with at least one year of experience.

Get in the car and forget about paid parking, maintenance, and other “fun parts” of being a car owner counting the insurance. All you need for an additional insurance package is one click in the Delimobil app.

You will find us in Moscow, Moscow and Tula oblast, Saint-Petersburg and Leningrad Oblast, Ekaterinburg, Krasnodar, Krasnoyarsk, Novosibirsk, Nizhniy Novgorod, Rostov-on-Don, Samara, Ufa, and Grozny.

Vehicle Fleet

There is a customized motor pool for each of the cities. We currently provide more than 10 000 cars, including compact Volkswagen Polos, posh BMWs, and colorful MINI Coopers. If you want to feel a little extra, take a Fiat 500 or a Smart.

How to start?

Signing up is easy: upload the necessary documents and add your debit/credit card information. You can start looking for a car as soon as you are done with the registration.

Parking

You can start and finish your ride within a specified area which you will find on the application map — it is colored mint and covers most parts of the city, including airports.

Our Inspiration

We constantly work on making our service better and easy-to-use. Your feedback is what keeps us growing and motivated for future accomplishments. So… Go ahead! You are the driver now.

title: Delimobil – carsharing app

creator: Carsharing Russia
descriptionHtml:
Delimobil is a per-minute rental service which you can use from 18 y.o. and immediately after getting a driving license. To drive in Moscow region, you need to be 19 y.o. and have at least 1-year driving experience.

Drive not thinking about paid parking, maintenance, refuel and other “pleasures” of car reality. Moreover, you don’t have to think about insurance – additional insurance turns on simply by one button in the app.

You could find us in Moscow region, St. Petersburg region, Tula, Ekaterinburg, Krasnodar, Novosibirsk, Nizhny Novgorod and Samara.


Fleet

Every city has an individual fleet. Currently we have more than 12k cars, including Volkswagen Polo, classy BMW and bright MINI Cooper. If you ever want a stylish holiday – take Fiat 500 or Smart.

How to use?

You need to sign up: upload photos of necessary docs and add a bank card. After activation you can immediately book a car.

Parking

Start and finish rent is possible within allowed zone. The zone is highlighted with green solid line and covers most of the city, even the airport territory

Our inspiration

We constantly work to make the service more convenient, but always aim for better. Your feedback helps to motivate and inspire our team to achieve new goals.

Delimobil – drive the life on your terms!
descriptionShort: Better than owning a car or getting a taxi! Moscow, St. Petersburg and more

Delimobil is a per-minute rental service which you can use from 18 y.o. and immediately after getting a driving license. To drive in Moscow region, you need to be 19 y.o. and have at least 1-year driving experience.

Drive not thinking about paid parking, maintenance, refuel and other “pleasures” of car reality. Moreover, you don’t have to think about insurance – additional insurance turns on simply by one button in the app.

You could find us in Moscow region, St. Petersburg region, Tula, Ekaterinburg, Krasnodar, Novosibirsk, Nizhny Novgorod and Samara.


Fleet

Every city has an individual fleet. Currently we have more than 12k cars, including Volkswagen Polo, classy BMW and bright MINI Cooper. If you ever want a stylish holiday – take Fiat 500 or Smart.

How to use?

You need to sign up: upload photos of necessary docs and add a bank card. After activation you can immediately book a car.

Parking

Start and finish rent is possible within allowed zone. The zone is highlighted with green solid line and covers most of the city, even the airport territory

Our inspiration

We constantly work to make the service more convenient, but always aim for better. Your feedback helps to motivate and inspire our team to achieve new goals.

Delimobil – drive the life on your terms!

title: Delimobil – carsharing app

creator: Carsharing Russia
descriptionHtml:
Delimobil is a convenient carsharing for the city. Carsharing is cars that can be borrowed through the app for a minute, hour, or day. Suitable for drivers over 18 years old, you will need a passport and driving license to sign up.

Here's how it works

You open the app, choose the nearest car and go where you want. Then you park and lock the car from your smartphone. And the cost of the rent is deducted from the card.

​​What's especially good

Minimum driving experience
We believe that after obtaining a driver's license, it is worth continuing to practice so as not to lose the skill. Let our cars be your first cars.

Personal price
The cost of a minute depends on how you behave while driving. If you drive carefully, the price will be lower.

Business access
Cars like BMW, Audi, and Mercedes-Benz open up to good drivers, regardless of the numbers in the passport and license. We hope you are one of those.

The ability to travel
Wherever you are planning to go, you can most likely get there by a delimobil. And if you are going to travel around the country, you will meet our cars in 11 cities.

​​What's just good

Independence
It is easier to have a lot of delimobils than to buy just one of your own cars. They do not need to be refueled, washed, repaired, and you do not need to pay for anything other than driving time.

Impressions
Trying different cars all the time is very exciting. Where do you want to start: with popular models like the Volkswagen Polo, BMW 3, Mercedes-Benz E-class or with the rather exclusive Fiat 500, MINI Cooper, Kia Stinger?

Saving
We have especially thought out a lot of tariffs so that every trip is profitable. With no exceptions.

__
When you download the app, we ask you to go through a simple registration. Leave your phone number, email and take a photo of two documents: passport and license. You can rest assured that the data is encrypted and stored securely with us. And documents are needed only to draw up a contract at a distance and check whether you can drive.
descriptionShort: Car rental in Moscow and cities

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We rejoice ourselves and share our enthusiasm, because only George Lucas' trilogy is better than a new inspection.
If the car had damages, now we show their photos in inspection. This means that you no longer have to look for them under the snow — everything is already displayed in the app. We didn't forget about smart search either: we added a bunch of synonyms to it in order to understand you perfectly and save your time.

Here's how it works

You open the app, choose the nearest car and go where you want. Then you park and lock the car from your smartphone. And the cost of the rent is deducted from the card.

​​What's especially good

Minimum driving experience
Let our cars be your first cars. Continue to practice after obtaining rights to maintain your skills. We know how important this is.

Personal price
The cost of a minute depends on how you behave while driving. If you drive carefully, the price will be lower.

Business access
Cars like BMW, Audi, and Mercedes-Benz open up to good drivers, regardless of the numbers in the passport and license. We hope you are one of those.

The ability to travel
Wherever you are planning to go, you can most likely get there by a delimobil. And if you are going to travel around the country, you will meet our cars in 11 cities.

​​What's just good

Independence
It is easier to have a lot of delimobils than to buy just one of your own cars. They do not need to be refueled, washed, repaired, and you do not need to pay for anything other than driving time.

Impressions
Trying different cars all the time is very exciting. Where do you want to start: with popular models like the Volkswagen Polo, BMW 3, Mercedes-Benz E-class or with the rather exclusive Fiat 500, MINI Cooper, Kia Stinger?

Saving
We have especially thought out a lot of tariffs so that every trip is profitable. With no exceptions.

When you download the app, we ask you to go through a simple registration. Leave your phone number, email and take a photo of two documents: passport and license.
